<p align="center"><h2><span id="title">Query raster values (Points)</span></h2><img id="icon" src="../icons/img_rastervalPoints.png" /></p>

<p><span id="section">Brief Description</span></p>

<p>Returns the values of the raster cells below a point layer</p>

<p><span id="section">Parameters</span></p>
<ul>
	<li><p>
		<span>[param] Input raster: </span>The raster layer to work on</p>
	</li>
	<li><p>
		<span>[param] Raster band: </span>Which band of the input raster should be used?</p>
	</li>
	<li><p>
		<span>[param] Input point layer: </span>A point layer</p>
	</li>
	<li><p>
		<span>[param] Output Table: </span>Output result</p>
	</li>	
</ul>

<p><span id="section">Limitations</span></p>
	<p>Very large raster layers might prevent this tool from running due to memory issues. Both layers need to have the projection.</p>
<p>
<span id="section">Info</span>
</p>

